76, \"to\": 181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The best male swimmer in the world and the best female swimmer in the world have several things in common.\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The best male swimmer\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 227}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 240}, {\"ngram\": \"the best female swimmer\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 268}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 281}, {\"ngram\": \"several things\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both are the children of Olympians.\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the children\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both have mastered what is considered the hardest event in the sport\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the 400-meter individual medley\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094to the point of establishing seemingly untouchable world records.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hardest event\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the 400-meter individual medley\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094to\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"seemingly untouchable world records\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both will head to the Summer Olympics as burgeoning heroes in their respective home countries.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"burgeoning heroes\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"their respective home countries\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those countries are France (for L\\u00c3\\u00a9on Marchand) and Canada (for Summer McIntosh).\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/