 {\"ngram\": \"Americans\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThere are three really, really tough things American swimmers are facing,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says NBC analyst and Olympic gold medalist Rowdy Gaines.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 873, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2712676011294789e-14, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 911, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.8925108400330629, \"rank\": 0.12043457081524718, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 949, \"end\": 961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rowdy Gaines\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThere\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"three really, really tough things\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOne is L\\u00c3\\u00a9on.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOne\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"L\\u00c3\\u00a9\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two is Summer.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Summer\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And three are the Australian women.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1013, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.8214947584880149, \"rank\": 0.21729317433546902, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve all three got the potential to win gold medals in events the Americans could win, if not for them.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The Aussies are at least a foreign threat of their own making, incubated and built on their continental landmass on the other side of the globe.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medals\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"the Americans\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"them.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"The Aussies\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"at least a foreign threat\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"their own making\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"their continental landmass\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"the other side\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand and McIntosh, not so much.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.438583513050301e-19, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old Marchand swam collegiately for Bob Bowman at Arizona State, then recentlyfollowed Bowman as a professional to Texas.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1372, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"score\": 0.9999841875191663, \"rank\": 1.5805130927358987e-05, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\"}, {\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.535572329505709e-11, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}, {\"begin\": 1423, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.535572329505709e-11, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}, {\"begin\": 1451, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"score\": 0.9999996189054217, \"rank\": 2.860054870445399e-07, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 22-year-old Marchand swam\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"Arizona State\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIntosh, just 17 years old, trains with the Sarasota Sharks club team in Florida.\\u00c2 The two also spent considerable time with their respective teams doing altitude training at the U.S. Olympic Training Center in Colorado Springs, Colo.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1694, \"enti