 4452, \"to\": 4464}, {\"ngram\": \"the international swimmers\", \"from\": 4504, \"to\": 4530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I get it.\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a bummer that the two best swimmers train in the United States but don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t compete for the United States.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The reality is this: No coach on the planet is going to turn down swimmers of the caliber of Marchand and McIntosh.\", \"from\": 4546, \"to\": 4778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4602, \"end\": 4615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999754959036242, \"rank\": 2.4504526071685605e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 4756, \"end\": 4764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999999953206498, \"rank\": 4.679267326923714e-09, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}, {\"begin\": 4769, \"end\": 4777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.438583513050301e-19, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4546, \"to\": 4552}, {\"ngram\": \"a bummer\", \"from\": 4553, \"to\": 4561}, {\"ngram\": \"the two best swimmers\", \"from\": 4567, \"to\": 4588}, {\"ngram\": \"The reality\", \"from\": 4662, \"to\": 4673}, {\"ngram\": \"No coach\", \"from\": 4683, \"to\": 4691}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 4695, \"to\": 4705