one\", \"from\": 13403, \"to\": 13411}, {\"ngram\": \"activities\", \"from\": 13423, \"to\": 13433}, {\"ngram\": \"obligations\", \"from\": 13438, \"to\": 13449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That includes home-schooling for Summer and a variety of sponsor and endorsement opportunities.\", \"from\": 13451, \"to\": 13546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home-schooling\", \"from\": 13465, \"to\": 13479}, {\"ngram\": \"Summer\", \"from\": 13484, \"to\": 13490}, {\"ngram\": \"a variety\", \"from\": 13495, \"to\": 13504}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsor and endorsement opportunities\", \"from\": 13508, \"to\": 13545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Already a well-established professional, Summer has shown no interest in swimming collegiately, according to Arckey.)\", \"from\": 13547, \"to\": 13665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Summer\", \"from\": 13589, \"to\": 13595}, {\"ngram\": \"no interest\", \"from\": 13606, \"to\": 13617}, {\"ngram\": \"Arckey\", \"from\": 13657, \"to\": 13663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThey\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve managed what could be a really crazy 17-year-old life,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Arckey says.\", \"from\": 13667, \"to\": 13750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThey\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 13667, \"to\": 13679}, {\"ngram\": \"a really crazy 17-year-old life\", \"from\": 13702, \"to\": 13733}, {\"ngram\": \"Arckey\", \"from\": 13738, \"to\": 13744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe is a kid, and it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s very refreshing, to be quite honest.\", \"from\": 13751, \"to\": 13815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe\", \"from\": 13751, \"to\": 13757}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 13761, \"to\": 13766}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 13772, \"to\": 13778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can become serious too soon, and she values her time away from the pool.\", \"from\": 13816, \"to\": 13891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her time\", \"from\": 13863, \"to\": 13871}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 13882, \"to\": 13890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhen she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s in the pool, she loves to work hard.\", \"from\": 13893, \"to\": 13945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhen\", \"from\": 13893, \"to\": 13900}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 13912, \"to\": 13920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has a smile on her face while doing the work, and it didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t matter how hard the work was.\", \"from\": 13946, \"to\": 14041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a smile\", \"from\": 13954, \"to\": 13961}, {\"ngram\": \"her face\", \"from\": 13965, \"to\": 13973}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 13986, \"to\": 13994}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 14028, \"to\": 14036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was probably the most astounding thing to me.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d By 2023, the McIntosh-Arckey alchemy was fully underway.She defeated Katie Ledecky in the 200 freestyle early that winter in Fort Lauderdale, the first time Ledecky had been beaten in the U.S. at a distance of 200 meters or more since \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009914.\", \"from\": 14042, \"to\": 14338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14166, \"end\": 14179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}, {\"begin\": 14222, \"end\": 14237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lauderdale_High_School\", \"score\": 0.8848089272585546, \"rank\": 0.12628832001053822, \"text\": \"Fort Lauderdale\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lauderdale_High_School\", \"dbpedi