alian Ariarne Titmusregained the 400 free record from McIntosh at the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009923 world championships, but McIntosh defended her titles in both the 200 fly and 400 IM.\", \"from\": 14566, \"to\": 14732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14625, \"end\": 14633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.438583513050301e-19, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}, {\"begin\": 14672, \"end\": 14680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.438583513050301e-19, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 400 free record\", \"from\": 14600, \"to\": 14619}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009923 world championships\", \"from\": 14637, \"to\": 14666}, {\"ngram\": \"her titles\", \"from\": 14690, \"to\": 14700}, {\"ngram\": \"both the 200 fly\", \"from\": 14704, \"to\": 14720}, {\"ngram\": \"400 IM\", \"from\": 14725, \"to\": 14731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was the springboard into what could be a Summer blockbuster in Paris.\", \"from\": 14733, \"to\": 14807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14801, \"end\": 14806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.284733258803123e-20, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the springboard\", \"from\": 14742, \"to\": 14757}, {\"ngram\": \"a Summer blockbuster\", \"from\": 14777, \"to\": 14797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Canadian trials in May, McIntosh blew away her own world record in the 400 IM, dropping it to 4:24.38.\", \"from\": 14809, \"to\": 14918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14816, \"end\": 14824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9933935071961459, \"rank\": 0.006650428813624435, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 14840, \"end\": 14848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.438583513050301e-19, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 14835, \"to\": 14838}, {\"ngram\": \"her own world record\", \"from\": 14859, \"to\": 14879}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400 IM\", \"from\": 14883, \"to\": 14893}, {\"ngram\": \"4:24.38\", \"from\": 14910, \"to\": 14917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only one female in the world has been within four seconds of that time in 2024, and that swimmer (Australia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Kaylee McKeown) is not entered in the event in Paris.\", \"from\": 14919, \"to\": 15084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15031, \"end\": 15045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaylee McKeown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\"}, {\"begin\": 15078, \"end\": 15083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.284733258803123e-20, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only one female\", \"from\": 14919, \"to\": 14934}, {\"ngram\": \"th