s\", \"from\": 15511, \"to\": 15524}, {\"ngram\": \"her weaker stroke\", \"from\": 15556, \"to\": 15573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s top two-three in the world in fly and free, top five or 10 in back.\", \"from\": 15606, \"to\": 15684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 15606, \"to\": 15616}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 15634, \"to\": 15643}, {\"ngram\": \"fly\", \"from\": 15647, \"to\": 15650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has so much easy speed the first half, especially the butterfly.\", \"from\": 15685, \"to\": 15753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much easy speed\", \"from\": 15693, \"to\": 15711}, {\"ngram\": \"the first half\", \"from\": 15712, \"to\": 15726}, {\"ngram\": \"especially the butterfly\", \"from\": 15728, \"to\": 15752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She gets to go out in her best stroke and just keep going.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The greater challenge will be handling the workload that comes with four individual events and likely relay duties.\", \"from\": 15754, \"to\": 15932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her best stroke\", \"from\": 15776, \"to\": 15791}, {\"ngram\": \"The greater challenge\", \"from\": 15816, \"to\": 15837}, {\"ngram\": \"the workload\", \"from\": 15855, \"to\": 15867}, {\"ngram\": \"four individual events\", \"from\": 15884, \"to\": 15906}, {\"ngram\": \"likely relay duties\", \"from\": 15911, \"to\": 15930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIntosh has dropped the 200 free but still is entered in the 400 freestyle, 200 butterfly and both IMs, which could necessitate 10 swims across eight days.\", \"from\": 15933, \"to\": 16089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15933, \"end\": 15941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.438583513050301e-19, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbped